(20, 'SỬA MÁY TÍNH QUẬN 6', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i sẽ c&oacute; mặt trong v&ograve;ng 40 ph&uacute;t di chuyển từ cty đến nơi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch cần trong quận 6</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">gi&aacute; dịch vụ sửa m&aacute;y vi t&iacute;nh&nbsp;tại nh&agrave; từ 100.000 - 200.000 VNĐ&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">=&gt; c&agrave;i đặt window c&ugrave;ng với đầy đủ ứng dụng cơ bản (c&agrave;i th&ecirc;m ứng dụng thiết kế đồ họa cộng th&ecirc;m 50.000 vnđ)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">+ m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh để b&agrave;n =&gt; 150.000 vnđ, &nbsp;+ laptop =&gt; 200.000 vnđ</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cung cấp linh kiện thay thế khi cần trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh Sửa M&aacute;y t&iacute;nh tại quận 6 cho nh&agrave; ri&ecirc;ng, c&ocirc;ng ty &amp; doanh nghiệp:</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(18, 36, 78);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Một Số linh kiện thường thay thế:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">- ch&aacute;y nguồn PC</span>&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">=&gt;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">thay thế nguồn 550W: 650.000 vnđ</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">- Lỗi Ram:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;=&gt; thay ram DDr2 bus800(</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">1GB 300.000 vnđ, 2G 550.000 vnđ</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;=&gt; thay ram&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">DDr3 bus 1333(2G 550.000 vnđ, 4G 850.000 vnđ)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">- hư hỏng Ổ cứng:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">=&gt; thay ổ cứng 80G 550.000 vnđ</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">=&gt; thay ổ cứng 160G 750.000 vnđ</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">=&gt; thay ổ cứng 250G 950.000 vnđ</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>- hư hỏng mainboard :</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">=&gt; thay mainboard G31 850.000 vnđ (bảo h&agrave;nh 24 th&aacute;ng)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">=&gt; thay mainboard G41 1.050.000 vnđ (bảo h&agrave;nh 24 th&aacute;ng)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">=&gt; thay mainboard H61 1.650.000 vnđ&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(bảo h&agrave;nh 24 th&aacute;ng)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 9pt 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><b style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">- hư hỏng ph&iacute;m chuột =&gt; thay chuột 100.000 vnđ t&ugrave;y loại, ph&iacute;m 200.000 vnđ t&ugrave;y loại</b></p>', 'SỬA MÁY TÍNH CHUYÊN NGHIỆP', ''),
